== Turn Order ==

* Based on Agility stat
* Higher agility acts first
* Enemies have own agility values
* Random variance each turn

== Commands ==

=== Fight ===

Physical attack with equipped weapon:
* Damage = Strength + Weapon - Defense
* Can miss based on target evasion
* Critical hits possible (Martial Artists have higher rate)

