=== Defend ===

Take defensive stance:
* Reduces damage taken
* Useful for vulnerable characters

=== Run ===

Attempt to flee:
* Success based on party vs enemy levels
* Boss battles may prevent running
* All party members must survive turn

=== Parry ===

Protect another party member:
* Hero takes attacks meant for target
* Useful for protecting mages/priests

